subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which famous fort is located in Jodhpur?
question_hi: जोधपुर में प्रत्येक अभिप्रकार का क्या फोट है?
explanation_en: Umaid Bhawan Palace is the famous palace located in Jodhpur. It was built by Maharaja Umaid Singh and is now a heritage hotel.
